  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package elevates Model Risk Level to 3 reflecting broader intended use across multiple device variants with higher decision consequence weighting. Thirteen credibility factors are addressed; two factors are marked not-assessed on the basis that they were considered beyond the scope of the current submission phase.",
