      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2) is a commercially validated code with documented SQA processes. Internal version-control logs and regression test suite results were reviewed and found compliant with the required gradation level."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
