      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions or equivalent benchmark confirms correct implementation of governing equations.",
      "rationale": "Verification via method of manufactured solutions was performed for the incompressible Navier-Stokes equations in rotating reference frames. Observed order of convergence matched theoretical order, confirming correct code implementation."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
